astraiea.layer1.varghaDelaney

Class VDmod

  • java.lang.Object
    • astraiea.layer1.varghaDelaney.VDmod
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ThresholdVDMod

    public abstract class VDmod
extends java.lang.Object
    Implementation of the Modified Vargha Delaney from .... . This modifies the comparison between individual results that is part of the Vargha Delaney process to ensure that this comparison is problem specific and excludes irrelevant differences. This class should be extended for your problem.
    Author:
    Geoffrey Neumann

      • compare

        public abstract Ordering compare(double tVal,
                                 double cVal)
        Will be called every time a result from one dataset is compared to one from another dataset as part of the Vargha Delaney comparison. Compares the two results to indicate which one is greater. Overwrite this method for a problem specific comparison.
        Parameters:
        tVal - first result
        cVal - second result
        Returns:
        GREATER if first result is greater, EQUAL if both results are equal and LOWER if first result is lower
